<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink397">
<l>kaviḻmayi reruttiṟ cennā yēṟṟai</l>
<l>kuruḷaip paṉṟi koḷḷātu kaḻiyuñ</l>
<l>curanaṉi vārā niṉṟaṉa ḷeṉpatu</l>
<l>muṉṉuṟa viraintanī ruraimi</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉakai muṟuvaleṉ ṉāyat tōrkkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O travelers walking ahead of us! </l>
<l>Please announce to my delicately smiling friends in town,</l>
<l>“She is approaching, after passing the wasteland, </l>
<l>where a male wild dog with hair on his neck, </l>
<l>moves away without killing a pig and her piglet”. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
